node.text:
Developed for the track, the KTM RC 8C is 100% race-ready!

Lightweight, powerful, and absolutely focused, this hand-built work of art is not for the faint hearted!

For more details on the KTM RC 8C project and how to pre-order, click the link in bio.

#KTM #ReadyToRace #KTMRC8C #RaceRC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KTM on July 20, 2021. May be an image of motorcycle and text.

node.text:
A bespoke chassis and a wealth of carefully chosen, high-end components come together to produce a 100% track-focused weapon! Weighing in at 140kg dry, and with the proven 128hp LC8c engine packing a serious punch, the KTM RC 8C is as close to a factory machine as you can get!

For more details on the KTM RC 8C project and how to pre-order, click the link in bio.

#KTM #ReadyToRace #KTMRC8C #RaceRC

node.text:
#KTMPowerParts - Enjoy increased braking performance for your KTM offroad machine with the WAVE BRAKE DISC. Featuring a floating design with a high-performance brake steel outer ring, and an inner ring of anodized aluminum, the disc resists warping, provides excellent, consistent braking, and looks great too!

For more info - click the link in bio!

#KTM #ReadyToRace #IntensifyYourRide
